]]''', Narrator. ''[[The English Spy]], Gabriel Allon, Book 15'' by [[Daniel Silva (novelist)|Daniel Silva]]. }}\n'''''Prior to 2016, this award category was titled: \"Solo Narration-Male\"'''''\n{{bulleted list\n|2015<ref name=\"Fifteen\"></ref>: '''[[Bronson Pinchot]]''', Narrator. ''The Hero's Guide to Being an Outlaw'' by Christopher Healy. \n|2014<ref name=\"Fourteen\"></ref>: '''[[David Pittu]]''', Narrator. ''[[The Goldfinch (novel)|The Goldfinch]]'' by [[Donna Tartt]]. \n|2013<ref name=\"BLR2013\"></ref>: '''[[Edoardo Ballerini]]''', Narrator.  ''[[Beautiful Ruins]]'' by [[Jess Walter]]. \n|2012<ref name=\"BLR2012\"></ref><ref name=\"Twelve\"></ref>: '''Simon Vance''', Narrator.  ''[[The King's Speech]]: How One Man Saved the British Monarchy'' by Mark Logue and [[Peter Conradi]]. \n|2011<ref name=\"BookListReader2011\"></ref>: '''[[Alan Cumming]]''', Narrator. ''[[Zorgamazoo]]'' by [[Robert Paul Weston]]. \n|2010<ref name=\"BLR2010\"></ref>: '''Charlton Griffin''', Narrator.  ''[[Great Expectations]]'' by [[Charles Dickens]]. \n|2009<ref name=\"BLR2009\"></ref>: '''John Lee''', Narrator.  ''[[The Count of Monte Cristo]]'' by [[Alexandre Dumas]].\n|2008<ref name=\"VOX2008\" />: '''[[Jim Dale]]''', Narrator. ''[[Harry Potter and The Deathly Hallows]]'' by [[J.K. Rowling]].\n|2007<ref name=\"IPOL2007\"></ref>: '''[[Jim Dale]]''', Narrator. ''[[Peter and the Shadow Thieves]]: The Starcatchers, Book 2'' by [[Dave Barry]] and [[Ridley Pearson]]. \n|2006<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: '''William Hootkins''', Narrator. ''Moby Dick'' by Herman Melville. \n|2005<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: '''[[Jim Dale]]''', Narrator. ''Peter and the Starcatchers'' by Dave Barry and Ridley Pearson.\n|2004<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: '''[[Will Patton]]''', Narrator. ''Last Car to Elysian Fields: A [[Dave Robicheaux]] Novel'' by [[James Lee Burke]]. \n|2003<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: '''[[Frank Muller]]''', Narrator. ''[[Tishomingo Blues (novel)|Tishomingo Blues]]'' by [[Elmore Leonard]].  \n|2002<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: '''[[Frank Muller]]''', Narrator. ''[[Coldheart Canyon]]: A Hollywood Ghost Story'' by [[Clive Barker]].\n|2001<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: '''[[Jim Dale]]''', Narrator. ''[[Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire]]'' by [[J. K. Rowling]].\n }}\n|-\n|'''Multi Voiced \n'''Performance'''\n|{{bulleted list\n|2019<ref name=\"Nineteen\"></ref>: ''Dreamland Burning'' by Jennifer Latham. Narrated by '''[[Pyeng Threadgill]]''' and '''Luke Slattery'''.\n|2018<ref name=\"Eighteen\"></ref>: ''Restart'' by [[Gordon Korman]]. Narrated by '''[[Jonathan Todd Ross]]''', '''Laura Knight Keating''', '''Ramon de Ocampo''', '''Andy Paris''', '''Suzy Jackson''', '''Graham Halstead''', and '''John Kroft'''.\n|2017<ref name=\"Seventeen\"></ref>: ''[[Small Great Things]]'' by [[Jodi Picoult]]. Narrated by '''[[Audra McDonald]]''', '''Cassandra Campbell''', and '''Ari Fliakos'''. \n|2016<ref name=\"Sixteen\"></ref>: ''[[Illuminae]]: The Illuminae Files, Book 1''  by [[Amie Kaufman]] and [[Jay Kristoff]]. Narrated by '''Olivia Taylor Dudley''', '''Lincoln Hoppe''', and '''[[Johnathan McClain]]'''.\n|2015<ref name=\"Fifteen\"></ref>: ''[[The Graveyard Book]]''  by [[Neil Gaiman]]. Narrated by a full cast including the author, '''Derek Jacobi''', '''Robert Madge''', '''[[Clare Corbett]]''', '''Miriam Margolyes''', '''Andrew Scott''', and '''Julian Hind-Tutt'''.\n|2014<ref name=\"Fourteen\"></ref>: ''[[World War Z]]: The Complete Edition: An Oral History of the Zombie War''  by [[Max Brooks]]. Narrated by '''[[Martin Scorsese]]''', '''[[Alfred Molina]]''', and a full cast.\n|2013<ref name=\"BLR2013\"></ref><ref name=\"Select2013\"></ref>: ''[[Dracula]]'' by [[Bram Stoker]], Narrated by '''[[Alan Cumming]]''', '''[[Tim Curry]]''', '''Simon Vance''', '''[[Katherine Kellgren]]''', '''[[Susan Duerden]]''', '''John Lee''', '''Graeme Malcolm''', '''Steven Crossley''', et al. \n|2012<ref name=\"BLR2012\"></ref>: ''[[A Raisin in the Sun]]'' by [[Lor