en, and Dion Graham. \n|2012<ref name=\"BLR2012\"></ref>: ''Selected Shorts: New American Stories'' by Aleksandar Hemon, Jhumpa Lahirir, Chimamanda Ngozi Adichie, and Sherman Alexie. Narrated by Boyd Gaines, Rita Wolf, Condola Rashad, and BD Wong. \n|2011<ref name=\"BookListReader2011\"></ref>: ''Stories: All-New Tales'' by Neil Gaiman. Narrated by Anne Bobby, Jonathan Davis, Peter Francis James, Katherine Kellgren, and Euan Morton. \n|2010<ref name=\"BLR2010\"></ref>: ''The Black Mask Audio Magazine, Vol. 1: Classic Hard-Boiled Tales From the Original Black Mask'' by Hugh B. Cave, Paul Cain, Frederick Nebel, Reuben J. Shay, Dashiell Hammett, and William Cole. Narrated by a full cast.\n|2009<ref name=\"BLR2009\"></ref>: ''[[Armageddon in Retrospect]]: And Other New and Unpublished Writings on War and Peace'' by [[Kurt Vonnegut]]. Narrated by Rip Torn and Michael Vonnegut.\n|2008<ref>{{cite web |title=Audible '20th Century Ghosts' [listing] |url=https://www.audible.com/pd/20th-Century-Ghosts-Audiobook/B0036KRFBI?ref=a_ep_audie-_c8_lProduct_15_9&pf_rd_p=bab774e3-a06e-4f9d-ba8e-5f2838406ba4&pf_rd_r=Z95GN0SJT6FM69X763SS |website=Audible.com |publisher=Audible, Inc. |accessdate=22 May 2019}}</ref>: ''[[20th Century Ghosts]]'' by [[Joe Hill (writer)|Joe Hill]]. Narrated by David Ledoux. \n|2007<ref name=\"IPOL2007\"></ref>: ''[[This I Believe]]: The Personal Philosophies of Remarkable Men and Women'' by [[Jay Allison]] and [[Dan Gediman]]. Narrated by Bill Gates, Martha Graham, et al.\n|2006<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: ''[[Runaway (book)|Runaway: Stories]]'' by [[Alice Munro]]. Narrated by Kymberly Dakin.\n|2005<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: ''[[Dress Your Family in Corduroy and Denim]]'' written and narrated by [[David Sedaris]].\n|2004<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: ''Home on the Prairie: Stories from [[Lake Wobegon]]'' written and narrated by [[Garrison Keillor]].\n|2003<ref name=\"LCLAudies\"></ref>: ''Classic Women's Short Stories'' by Katherine Mansfield, Kate C